Initial release source-data confirmation:

The initial public release includes catalog records and source-record
measurements imported from the local PIG / Jaskinie Polski and TPN exports.
The project maintainer confirmed on 2026-05-16 that these data may be
redistributed as part of this public repository and its generated release
artifacts under CC BY 4.0.

Attribution should retain the source references already recorded in YAML
records and generated exports, including PIG catalog identifiers, PIG links,
TPN GLOBALID values, and NR_INWENT inventory references where present.
